## Part 2 — ✨ New Feature: Daily Planner (Day Blocks + Tasks)

### Database — DB v7 → v8

#### [MODIFY] [database.dart](file:///e:/2026/MyBigProjects_SimpleLib/TrackerTime/lib/core/db/database.dart)

**New Table: `DayBlocks`** — Global day segment templates

| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | TEXT PK | UUID |
| `name` | TEXT | e.g. "الصباح", "بعد الشغل" |
| `icon` | TEXT | Icon key |
| `color` | INTEGER | ARGB |
| `sortOrder` | INTEGER | 0, 1, 2… |
| `isArchived` | BOOLEAN | default false |
| `createdAt` | DATETIME | — |
| `updatedAt` | DATETIME | — |

**New Table: `DayTasks`** — Per-date tasks inside a block

| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | TEXT PK | UUID |
| `blockId` | TEXT FK → DayBlocks | Which block |
| `activityId` | TEXT? FK → Activities | Optional timer link |
| `date` | TEXT | `YYYY-MM-DD` — tasks are per-day |
| `title` | TEXT | Task description |
| `isCompleted` | BOOLEAN | default false |
| `sortOrder` | INTEGER | Order within block |
| `completedAt` | DATETIME? | Set when checked |
| `createdAt` | DATETIME | — |
| `updatedAt` | DATETIME | — |

**Migration `from < 8`**:
```dart
if (from < 8) {
  await m.createTable(dayBlocks);
  await m.createTable(dayTasks);
  // Seed 3 default blocks
  await _seedDefaultBlocks(m);
}
```
Default seeded blocks:
- 🌅 الصباح (sortOrder: 0, amber)
- 💼 وقت العمل (sortOrder: 1, blue)
- 🌙 المساء (sortOrder: 2, indigo)

